Package schedule.filter

Record Class ProfessorFilter

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
schedule.filter.ProfessorFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Predicate<Lecture>, Filter
public record ProfessorFilter(String requirement) extends Record implements Filter
Represents a filter that checks if a lecture's professor matches a requirement.

Returns true if the lecture's professor contains the requirement.

Implements the Filter interface.
